"The pre-configured ratings are :guilabel:`Needs Improvement`, "
":guilabel:`Meets Expectations`, :guilabel:`Exceeds Expectations`, and "
":guilabel:`Strongly Exceeds Expectations`. To add another rating, click the "
":guilabel:`New` button."
